tional and high net worth clients” said owen thomas president of morgan stanley investment management msim offers clients a comprehensive family of bond equity and multiasset class products as well as private partnerships that invest in private equity venture capital and real estate opportunities  morgan stanley investment management together with its investment advisory affiliates has over  investment professionals around the world and us billion in assets under management or supervision as of february    these entities offer investment management services to a diverse client base which includes governments institutions corporations and individuals morgan stanley is a leading global financial services firm providing a wide range of investment banking securities investment management wealth management and credit services  the firm’s employees serve clients worldwide including corporations governments institutions and individuals from more than  offices in  countries  for further information about morgan stanley please visit wwwmorganstanleycomnote to editorsblair pickerellprior to this appointment blair pickerell was chief executive asia pacific of hsbc investments hong kong ltd mr pickerell received his ba and ma from stanford university and his mba from harvard business school   he joined the jardine matheson group in  and in  set up the jardine fleming office in taiwan where he played an active role in the development of its mutual fund industry   mr pickerell returned to hong kong in  and spent two years at mandarin oriental hotel group before returning to jardine fleming as general manager of jardine fleming unit trusts limited  in  he was appointed managing director of jardine pacific limited a hong kongbased conglomerate with  staff in over  countries with operations in industries ranging from consumer goods financial services and restaurants to engineering transportation and security in august  he rejoined jf asset management as managing director and as chairman of jf funds limited he joined hsbc investments in may  and was a member of the firm’s global management committee mr pickerell lives in hong kong with his family  he speaks and reads mandarincontact media relations nick footitt                                       poling cheung  close morgan stanley  press release  blair pickerell to head morgan stanley investment management in asia press releases email article printer friendly blair pickerell to head morgan stanley investment management in asia apr    hong kong   morgan stanley nyse ms today announced the appointment of blair pickerell as a managing director and head of morgan stanley investment management msim for asia  mr pickerell who will be based in hong kong and starts in his new role in june will also be a member of the firm’s asia executive committee and the msim senior management committee  he joins from hsbc where he was responsible for the bank’s investment management business in the asia region hans schuettler chief executive officer morgan stanley asia said “with growing global interest in asia with regional markets opening up and with the increasing sophistication of institutional and individual investors the region is a critical growth opportunity for our asset management business clients are looking for bestinclass asset management products and under blair’s leadership we are confident that we will continue to deliver” “with over  years in asia blair’s regional and product experience will be invaluable as we grow our business geographically and expand the range of asset classes and investment strategies we offer to institutional and high net worth clients” said owen thomas president of morgan stanley investment management msim offers clients a comprehensive family of bond equity and multiasset class products as well as private partnerships that invest in private equity venture capital and real estate opportunities  morgan stanley investment management together with its investment advisory affi